<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-12-20T05:00:00-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-12-20T05:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-20T05:00:00-05:00</updated><title>拜登政府制定了一项新战略，为基层环保组织提供联邦资金</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 对着麦克风讲话，迈克尔·里根 (Michael Regan) 坐在她旁边。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/W8TAJ0G4pZuYNX8oZUZrAEI3iVA=/0x24:3000x2024/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72981499/1246597403.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption >;&lt;em>;1 月 27 日星期五，美国副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris)（右）和美国环境保护署 (EPA) 局长迈克尔·里根 (Michael Regan)（左）在华盛顿特区艾森豪威尔行政办公大楼举行的活动中2023 年。&lt;/em>; |图片：Jemal Countess / UPI / Bloomberg via Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;j5vzvs&quot;>;环境保护局&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.epa.gov/newsroom&quot;>;命名&lt;/a>; 今天有 11 个“资助者”，即大学和非营利组织，将负责向当地主导的环境项目发放 6 亿美元的联邦资金。这是一项新战略，旨在让小型草根团体——尤其是那些污染最严重的团体——更容易获得资金。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;nVbA9e&quot;>;这些团体将能够向 EPA 资助者申请次级赠款，这些资助者已被指派负责监督某些地区的资金。这 11 家资助者包括一些与美国环境种族主义和不公正现象作斗争的最杰出人士。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5Bs46M&quot;>;其中包括气候正义联盟 (CJA)，该联盟由来自全球各地的成员组织组成。美国 - 来自布鲁克林最古老的...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/20/24008381/epa-grantmakers-harris-biden-administration-environmental -justice&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/20/24008381/epa-grantmakers-harris-biden-administration-environmental-justice" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/20/24008381/epa-grantmakers-harris-biden-administration-environmental-justice</id><author><name>贾斯汀·卡尔玛</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-20T04:35:11-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-20T04:35:11-05:00</updated><title> VanMoof 2.0：新的希望</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一张 VanMoof 电动自行车的放大照片，从后灯看过去 VanMoof 标志，沿着上管看到地平线上远处的一艘船。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/aCalJ9T6krSZLGWmC8TE_qVF9to=/529x0:3280x1834/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72981491/IMG20230507180027.0.jpeg ” />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;摄影：Thomas Ricker / The Verge&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;这家电动自行车公司的新领导层概述了其破产后计划，以重新启动并扩展到更多电子领域。移动性。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24009091/vanmoof-scooter-next-steps-parts-service-e-bikes&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24009091/vanmoof-scooter-next-steps-parts-service-e-bikes" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24009091/vanmoof-scooter-next-steps-parts-service-e-bikes</id><author><name>托马斯·瑞克</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T20:36:57-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T20:36:57-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年最受欢迎的值得挥霍的礼物</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;各种产品的照片插图，背景为明亮的星星图形。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/LeMh_lYwSS716rkGuwdzNMqNLuA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72937150/236830_WORTH_THE_SPLURGE_Gift_Guide _Art_CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;当金钱不再是问题时，天空就是极限，所以为什么要将辛苦赚来的现金和硬币浪费在日常必需品上？是时候实现远大梦想了。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23920823/expense-holiday-gifts-wishes-extravagant-ideas-presents-2023&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23920823/expensive-holiday-gifts-wishes-extravagant-ideas-presents-2023" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23920823/expense-holiday-gifts-wishes-extravagant-ideas-presents-2023</id><author><name>边缘人员</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T19:21:31-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T19:21:31-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年游戏和娱乐节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Oziq9Th2P1ckSgzRT0ZYrugXX8Y=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72871362/236830_GAME_AND_ENT_2_Gift_Guide_Artboards_ CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;即使有人喜欢购买所有最新的大型游戏，我们也确信我们可以帮助您找到它们这个节日的独特且足够极客的礼物。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23959483/gaming-entertainment-gifts-ideas-2023-playstation-nintendo-xbox-tv -accessories&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23959483/gaming-entertainment-gifts-ideas-2023-playstation-nintendo-xbox-tv-accessories" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23959483/gaming-entertainment-gifts-ideas-2023-playstation-nintendo-xbox-tv-accessories</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T19:09:17-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T19:09:17-05:00</updated><title> Rite Aid 因“鲁莽”使用而被禁止面部识别五年</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;店面显示 Rite Aid 徽标的照片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AeTWd__w34__8LukewcEYZ8OAxE=/0x2:5000x3335/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn。 com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72980735/1258931679.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Getty&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;tDYeoq&quot;>;Rite Aid 不允许使用人工智能面部护理作为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ftc.gov/news-events/news/press-releases/2023/12/rite-aid-banned-using-ai-facial- 的一部分，识别技术再延长五年recognize-after-ftc-says-retailer-deployed-technology-without?utm_campaign=rite_aid_banned_from_usin&amp;amp;utm_content=1703022035&amp;amp;utm_medium=social&amp;amp;utm_source=twitter&quot;>;与联邦贸易委员会达成和解&lt;/a>;。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ftc.gov/system/files/ftc_gov/pdf/2023190_riteaid_complaint_filed.pdf&quot;>;周二提交的一份投诉&lt;/a>;中，FTC 指控 Rite Aid 在从 2012 年到 2020 年，这种行为“鲁莽”。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZmAQEx&quot;>;联邦贸易委员会表示，在此期间，Rite Aid 使用面部识别技术“捕获所有进入或穿过商店的消费者的图像” ”。据称，该公司随后创建了一个数据库，其中包含被识别为入店行窃者或表现出其他可疑行为的客户。对于某些顾客来说，数据库会包含“附带信息”，例如姓名、出生日期以及商店认为可疑的活动……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008516/rite-aid-facial-recognition-ban-ftc- Five-years&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008516/rite-aid-facial-recognition-ban-ftc-five-years" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008516/rite-aid-facial-recognition-ban-ftc- Five-years</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T18:55:16-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T18:55:16-05:00</updated><title> Epic不会禁止仅限成人分级的区块链游戏</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Epic Games 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/fE6sbLLp1sYsKePh31drYRi8o54=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/72980707/acastro_STK108__01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UJCSlV&quot;>;区块链游戏正在重返 Epic Games 市场。 Epic Games Store 严格禁止被娱乐软件评级委员会 (ESRB) 归类为“仅限成人”的游戏——通常是过度裸露或暴力的游戏。但市场今天&lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/RQGGzWGeG8&quot;>;宣布&lt;/a>;，区块链游戏被归类为 AO &lt;em>;仅仅是因为&lt;/em>;它们使用区块链，这是此规则的例外。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;ld6s0b&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>; 注意：Gods Unchained 和 Striker Manager 3 已于我们对基于区块链的游戏评级的内容政策进行了更改。了解更多信息：&lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/RQGGzWGeG8&quot;>;https://t.co/RQGGzWGeG8&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>;— Epic Games Store (@EpicGames) &lt;a href=&quot;https ://twitter.com/EpicGames/status/1737200788622225625?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;2023 年 12 月 19 日&lt;/a>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;4a5mVV&quot;>;“一些基于区块链的游戏正在接受行业评级机构针对其特定内容的仅限成人 (AO) 评级&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008602/epic- games-store-adults-only-blockchain-games&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008602/epic-games-store-adults-only-blockchain-games" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008602/epic-games-store-adults-only-blockchain-games</id><author><name>阿姆丽塔·哈立德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T18:38:19-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T18:38:19-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年家居科技节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手拿着不同的产品，背景是色彩鲜艳的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/E-LpdUcMKJSz2TPCi6T59dz2TjI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72842014/236830_HOME_TECH_Gift_Guide_Artboards_CV irginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从变色灯到为您和您的宠物准备晚餐的小工具，这里有一些我们最喜欢的智能家居礼物。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23933231/smart-home-tech-gift-guide-2023-video-doorbells-plugs-机器人吸尘器&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23933231/smart-home-tech-gift-guide-2023-video-doorbells-plugs-robot-vacuums" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23933231/smart-home-tech-gift-guide-2023-video-doorbells-plugs-robot-vacuums</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T18:35:47-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T18:35:47-05:00</updated><title> FBI 取缔后勒索软件团伙“夺取”其网站并发出新威胁</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;卡通插图显示一个阴影人物正在搬运一个红色目录文件夹，文件夹的侧面有一张惊讶的脸。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TyuvsoYQ2yezkG_LZIchtSqYfuU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72980665/VRG_Illo_STK001_B_Sala_Hacker.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：Beatrice Sala&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;DrwYiD&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/justice-department-disrupts-prolific -alphvblackcat-ransomware-variant&quot;>;美国司法部 (DOJ) 表示&lt;/a>;，作为跨国执法行动的一部分，FBI 已创建了一款解密工具，帮助其返回 500 多名勒索软件受害者的数据。它还写道，该局查获了由 ALPHV / Blackcat 勒索软件团伙运营的“几个网站”。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;8iUUQ0&quot;>;但是，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/ news/security/fbi-disrupts-blackcat-ransomware-operation-creates-decryption-tool/&quot;>;&lt;em>;电脑发出响声&lt;/em>;报告&lt;/a>;，截至今天下午，ALPHV / Blackcat 声称已重新控制其网站，FBI 仅拥有 400 家左右公司的解密密钥，导致 3,000 多名受害者的数据仍处于加密状态。据报道，该团伙还表示，不再限制分支机构使用其勒索软件攻击关键基础设施，包括医院和核电站。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;CQSP0G&quot;>;据...&lt;/p>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008093/alphv-blackcat-ransomware-gang-site-seized-fbi-doj&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008093/alphv-blackcat-ransomware-gang-site-seized-fbi-doj" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008093/alphv-blackcat-ransomware-gang-site-seized-fbi-doj</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T17:51:52-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T17:51:52-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年 PC 礼品指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星图形背景。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NKp7YtAgU_mcPIzB9I2SJBfnyLU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72825088/236830_PC_Gift_Guide_Art_CVirginia_LEDE _2040x1360.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;对于那些花太多时间坐在笔记本电脑或台式电脑上的人来说，这是最好的科技礼物——无论是工作还是工作休闲。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content-creator-tech-gadgets&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content-creator-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content-creator-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T17:29:57-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T17:29:57-05:00</updated><title>苹果的 iPhone 卫星系统为路边援助提供了新选项</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片显示用户成功连接到范围内的卫星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TD5IlNZoDBV6H77OyPswizhZmxE=/0x390:1125x1140/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72980452/IMG_0384.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;5xFYwf&quot;>;如果您拥有 iPhone 14 或 iPhone 15，您现在可以使用卫星连接访问 Verizon 的路边援助服务。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://support.apple.com/en-us/105098&quot;>;支持页面&lt;/a>;中&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.macrumors.com/2023/12/19 /verizon-roadside-assistance-apple-satellite/&quot;>;MacRumors 发现，Apple 现在表示您可以在运行 iOS 17.2（或更高版本）和 Verizon 的设备上利用该功能SIM 卡。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Si16ez&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.verizon。 com/solutions-and-services/add-ons/safety/roadside-assistance?cjdata=MXxOfDB8WXww&amp;URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verizon.com%2Fsolutions-and-services%2Fadd-ons%2Fsafety%2Froadside-援助&amp;CMP=afc_h_p_cj_oth_fios_2022_04&amp;amp;SID=73726X1523000X36f0f597c3d5345bd2380d3050ee18aa&amp;cjevent=77b905989ead11ee832200e30a82b82c&amp;amp;vendorid=C JM&amp;amp;PID=100045529&amp;amp;AID=11557999#overview&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Verizon 的路边援助计划&lt;/a>;由 Allstate 旗下的 Signature Motor Club 运营，在您遇到汽车故障时提供帮助，即使您开的是朋友的车或租来的车。它包括向任何方向拖曳车辆长达 10 英里、绞车、燃油输送、跨接启动、轮胎服务等。虽然 Verizon 提供每条线路每月 4.99 美元的订阅费，但它还 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.verizon.com/support /roadside-assistance-faqs/&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;为未订阅而使用该服务的 Verizon 客户提供固定费用&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;NbyJmb&quot; >;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/12/23870328/apple-iphone-roadside-assistance-emergency-sos-satellite-aaa&quot;>;一个...&lt;/a>;&lt; /p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008362/apple-iphone-verizon-roadside-assistance-satellite&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008362/apple-iphone-verizon-roadside-assistance-satellite" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008362/apple-iphone-verizon-roadside-assistance-satellite</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>